```

Displays:

- Ray cluster status
- Available resources (CPU/GPU/memory)
- Active jobs
- GPU utilization
- System metrics

### Web Dashboards

| Service       | URL                        | Purpose                         |
| ------------- | -------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Ray Dashboard | http://localhost:8265      | Job monitoring, logs, resources |
| API Docs      | http://localhost:8266/docs | REST API documentation          |
| MLflow UI     | http://localhost:8080      | Experiments, models, artifacts  |

### Resource Usage

```python
from api.client import RayComputeClient

client = RayComputeClient()
resources = client.get_resources()

print(f"GPU Utilization: {resources['gpus'][0]['gpu_utilization']}%")
print(f"GPU Memory Used: {resources['gpus'][0]['memory_used_mb']} MB")
print(f"Available CPUs: {resources['available']['cpu']}")
```

