## 🛠️ Maintenance

### Update Docker Images

```bash
cd docker
./build_images.sh
```

### Restart Services

```bash
# Restart Ray
./scripts/stop_ray.sh
./scripts/start_ray_head.sh

# Restart API
pkill -f "python3 server.py"
cd api && python3 server.py &
```

### Clean Up Old Jobs

```bash
# Delete completed jobs
python3 -c "
from api.client import RayComputeClient
client = RayComputeClient()
jobs = client.list_jobs(status='SUCCEEDED')
for job in jobs:
    client.delete_job(job['job_id'])
"
```

